tafsir[3]{c,v,t}:
  40,59,"The Hour will certainly come: Therein is no doubt: Yet most men believe not."
  40,60,"And your Lord says: \"Call on Me; I will answer your (Prayer): but those who are too arrogant to serve Me will surely find themselves in Hell - in humiliation!\""
  40,63,"Thus are deluded those who are wont to reject the Signs of Allah."